name: BetaPro Silver 2x Daily Bull ETF
longDescription: SLVU seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the daily performance of its Referenced Futures Index. SLVU is denominated in Canadian dollars. SLVU does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
